
1.
Feature: Boarding screen functionalities
Given user is on the boarding screen of drest mobile app
And user can see some information with sliding text points 
When user swipe swipes right to left
Then next screen comes with more information 
When user swipes slide points again
Then next user can see more information box 
And user can see Log in box button
And user can see Join button

2.
Feature: Register functionalities as a guest
Given user is onboarding screen
When user tap on Join button
Then Create account screen pops up
When user taps on policy and promotion box
And user ticks the Terms and services
And the play as a guest box becomes active 
When User taps Play as a guest button
Then user navigates to Home screen/ Tutorial screen

3.
Feature: Post registration 
Given I register successfully as a User
And I am on the Homescreen/Tutorial Challenge screen
And a message pops up with tap to continue active write
When I tap on Tap to continue an information box pops up
And I tap on the screen 
Then the information box disapears

